text: Dominic Francis Perrottet ( ; born 21 September 1982) is an Australian politician. He was the 46th premier of New South Wales and Leader of the New South Wales division of the Liberal Party of Australia from 2021 to 2023. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Premiers of New South Wales Category:Australian lawyers Category:Politicians from Sydney Category:Liberal Party of Australia politicians
